# Stock Scrapper requires no API keys, access tokens, or paid credentials.
# Runtime configuration is read from config/settings.yaml,
# config/scoring_rules.yaml, config/backtesting_rules.yaml, and
# config/watchlist.csv. Local state is stored in data/market.db.
#
# The application does not currently load values from a .env file. This file
# exists only to make the credential-free local setup explicit; copying it to
# .env is unnecessary.
